ADDITIONAL QUICK REFERENCE
========================================

**Most Asked Topics:**
- Binary Search
- Sorting Algorithms
- Linked Lists and Arrays
- Tree Traversals
- Graph Algorithms
- SQL Queries
- REST API Concepts
- OOP Principles

**Preparation Tips:**
- Practice coding problems on platforms like LeetCode or HackerRank
- Master at least 2-3 programming languages
- Understand the time and space complexity of each solution
- Be ready to explain your thought process
- Have 2-3 mini projects ready to discuss
- Practice common HR questions
- Take mock interviews

**Time Management:**
- Spend 10 mins on introduction
- Spend 20 mins explaining your coding solution
- Spend 30 mins on DSA, Database, and Web Technology questions
- Spend 10-15 mins on HR questions
- Keep 5 mins buffer for any follow-up questions
